engrossed-amendment-form.current-chamber: In the Senate of the United States,

section.text: That the resolution from the House of Representatives (H. Con. Res. 90) entitled Concurrent resolution directing the Secretary of the Senate to make a technical correction in the enrollment of S. 1356., do pass with the following

amendment-instruction.text: Strike the matter following the resolving clause and insert the following:

amendment-block.continuation-text: That in the enrollment of the bill S. 1356, the Secretary of the Senate shall make the following corrections:

paragraph.text: Amend the title so as to read: An Act to authorize appropriations for fiscal year 2016 for military activities of the Department of Defense, for military construction, and for defense activities of the Department of Energy, to prescribe military personnel strengths for such fiscal year, and for other purposes..
In the table of contents in section 2, in the item relating to section 1242, amend Ukrainian Republic so as to read Ukraine.
In the table of contents for title XII before section 1201, in the item relating to section 1242, amend Ukrainian Republic so as to read Ukraine.
In the section heading of section 1242, amend Ukrainian Republic so as to read Ukraine.
In section 1242, amend the Ukrainian Republic so as to read Ukraine each place it appears in subsections (a)(1) and (b).
Strike section 4201 and insert the following:
